{"book": 23, "chapter": 6, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "主呼召以賽亞作先知"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "當烏西雅王崩的那年，我見主坐在高高的寶座上。他的衣裳垂下，遮滿聖殿。 "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "其上有撒拉弗侍立，各有六個翅膀：用兩個翅膀遮臉，兩個翅膀遮腳，兩個翅膀飛翔； "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "彼此呼喊說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "聖哉！聖哉！聖哉！萬軍之耶和華；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的榮光充滿全地！"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因呼喊者的聲音，門檻的根基震動，殿充滿了煙雲。 "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時我說：「禍哉！我滅亡了！因為我是嘴唇不潔的人，又住在嘴唇不潔的民中，又因我眼見大君王－萬軍之耶和華。」"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "有一撒拉弗飛到我跟前，手裏拿着紅炭，是用火剪從壇上取下來的， "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "將炭沾我的口，說：「看哪，這炭沾了你的嘴，你的罪孽便除掉，你的罪惡就赦免了。」 "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我又聽見主的聲音說：「我可以差遣誰呢？誰肯為我們去呢？」我說：「我在這裏，請差遣我！」 "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他說：「你去告訴這百姓說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們聽是要聽見，卻不明白；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "看是要看見，卻不曉得。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "要使這百姓心蒙脂油，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耳朵發沉，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "眼睛昏迷；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "恐怕眼睛看見，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耳朵聽見，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "心裏明白，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "回轉過來，便得醫治。」"}]}, {"type": "paragraph-no-indent", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我就說：「主啊，這到幾時為止呢？」他說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "直到城邑荒涼，無人居住，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "房屋空閒無人，地土極其荒涼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "並且耶和華將人遷到遠方，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在這境內撇下的地土很多。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "境內剩下的人若還有十分之一，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也必被吞滅，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "像栗樹、橡樹雖被砍伐，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "樹墩子卻仍存留。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這聖潔的種類在國中也是如此。"}]}]}